  m_Name: BirthDayCard
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DocumentItem
  documentTitle: 
  documentText: "I made this for Mama last year on August 28th, before my math test.
    I thought she would like the vanilla cake drawing because that\u2019s her favorite
    flavor. But she tore it up and said I should have spent that time studying instead.
    Maybe she\u2019ll like it this year. If I do better. If I make it prettier."
